Verify pprof installation

Source: R/sitrep.R
pprof_sitrep.Rd

Check if pprof and its dependencies are installed.

pprof_sitrep()

Examples

pprof_sitrep()

#> ● Call test_pprof() to test installation.
#> 
#> ── Requirements ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#> ✖ pprof missing ''
#> ● See <https://github.com/google/pprof> to install pprof.
#> ✖ Graphviz missing ''
#> ● See <https://www.graphviz.org/download> to install Graphviz.
#> 
#> ── Go ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#> ✔ Go binary /usr/local/bin/go
#> ℹ Go folder missing /Users/runner/go
#> ● See <https://golang.org/doc/install> to install Go.
#> ● If the Go folder is missing but the Go binary is non-missing, you may need
#>   to configure the GOPATH environment variable. See
#>   <https://github.com/golang/go/wiki/GOPATH>.
#> 
#> ── Custom ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#> ℹ `PROFFER_PPROF_BIN` missing ''
#> ● Run `usethis::edit_r_environ()` to edit '.Renviron' file.
#> ● PROFFER_PPROF_BIN=''
#> ℹ `PROFFER_GO_BIN` missing ''
#> ● Run `usethis::edit_r_environ()` to edit '.Renviron' file.
#> ● PROFFER_GO_BIN=/usr/local/bin/go
#> ℹ `PROFFER_GRAPHVIZ_BIN` missing ''
#> ● Run `usethis::edit_r_environ()` to edit '.Renviron' file.
#> ● PROFFER_GRAPHVIZ_BIN=''
#> 
#> ── System ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#> ℹ pprof system path missing ''
#> ● See <https://github.com/google/pprof> to install pprof.
#> ✔ Go binary system path /usr/local/bin/go
#> ℹ Graphviz system path missing ''
#> ● See <https://www.graphviz.org/download> to install Graphviz.
#> 
#> ── Deprecated ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#> ✔ `pprof_path` env variable omitted.
